{"article_id":"w1Ea6LSLXcpe3J00","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Republicans say","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Senate briefing on Bergdahl does n't stem their skepticism","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"A video shows the minutes","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"before Bergdahl is swooped away by a Black Hawk chopper","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Taliban members shake hands with men from the Black Hawk","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Bergdahl 's hometown cancels an event","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"planned to celebrate his return","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Dressed in all white with a striped shawl across his shoulders , the gaunt American looks up at the Black Hawk chopper","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"circling overhead .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Armed Taliban men stand around him ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"one with a rocket-propelled grenade launcher ready .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"When the chopper lands ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"the American is led there by two men ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"one","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"carrying a white flag .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"He is given a pat-down ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"loaded on to the helicopter","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and whisked away .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"A new video","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"released by the Taliban","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"showed the final moments of Army Sgt . Bowe Bergdahl 's five years in captivity ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"just before he was handed over to the United States .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"As debate over the circumstances","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"surrounding Bergdahl 's release","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"showed no signs of slowing Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the video revealed intriguing clues about Bergdahl , his Taliban captors and his American rescuers .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The narration on the video says","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"the transfer took place in Khost province , in eastern Afghanistan .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"`` We had a number of tribal elders with us ...","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"in order to build trust between us and the other side , ''","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"a voice in the video says .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"JUST WATCHED Bergdahl swap from mouth of the Taliban","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Bergdahl swap from mouth of the Taliban 04:02","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Video released of Bergdahl 's transfer","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Video released of Bergdahl 's transfer 04:45","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"`` We told them","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"that we had warned all our Mujahideen fighters in Khost province and especially in Batai area not to attack them . ''","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"The 17-minute video also showed an unusual sight :","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Taliban members shaking hands with men from the Black Hawk .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The Pentagon said Wednesday","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"it has no reason","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"to doubt the video 's authenticity .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"`` But we are reviewing it , ''","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Pentagon spokesman Rear Adm. John Kirby said .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"`` Regardless , we know","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"the transfer was peaceful and successful ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"and our focus remains on getting Sgt . Bergdahl the care","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"he needs . ''","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Mike Baker , a former covert operations officer for the CIA , said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"there 's a clear purpose behind the video .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"`` The Taliban does n't operate in a bubble .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"They do n't live in a cave .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"They understand the importance of social media .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"They understand the importance of marketing and public relations , ''","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"he told CNN 's Brooke Baldwin .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"`` This is a scripted propaganda piece for them . ...","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"And so they 're doing this , in a sense ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"to show their credibility ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"to show their strength as warriors to their supporters ,","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"and to try to use it as a recruiting tool . ''","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"At one point in the video , Taliban members start chanting ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"`` Long live Mujahideen of Afghanistan , long live Mullah Omar , the leader of Taliban . ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"The narrator 's voice said","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"armed fighters were stationed throughout the transfer area .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"`` We waited in the area for around 10 minutes","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"before the helicopters arrived ,","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"and there were 18 Mujahideen fighters with me in the area , ''","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"the narrator said .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"Indeed , the video showed armed men perched high and low on nearby hillsides .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"`` Our arrangement was that","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"once the helicopters are on the ground ,","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"three people from the other side would get off the helicopter","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"and three from our side ,","depth":16},{"id":79,"text":"including the captive ,","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"would move toward the helicopter","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"to hand him over . ''","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"The video has few words in English , other than this message","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"superimposed over Bergdahl :","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Carney defends Bergdahl prisoner swap","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Carney defends Bergdahl prisoner swap","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"02:45","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"In the video , the narrator also gives his opinion about an issue","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that 's become a focal point since Bergdahl 's release :","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"the soldier 's health .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"`` They first asked us about the health condition of the captive","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and told us to tell them the truth","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"if he was not well ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"but we saw him ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"that he was fine ,","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"and we told them that , ''","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"the narrator says .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"Since announcing Bergdahl 's release over the weekend ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Obama administration officials have repeatedly said","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"they fast-tracked the operation over concerns about his health and safety ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"which appeared to be in jeopardy .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Recent intelligence , in addition to two proof-of-life videos of Bergdahl","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"released in recent months ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"led to growing concern about his health and safety ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"a senior defense official said Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Chris Voss , the FBI 's former lead international hostage negotiator , said","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"that might have been exactly what Bergdahl 's captors wanted .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"`` You expect the hostage-takers to make it look like the hostage is in bad shape","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"so that they can drive a better bargain ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"and clearly it looks to me that 's what they did here , ''","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"he told CNN 's `` The Lead with Jake Tapper '' on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"National Security Adviser Susan Rice said","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Bergdahl served with honor and distinction .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"But there 's a growing chorus of criticism from some","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"who served with him ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"describing him as a deserter","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"`` I believe","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"that he totally deserted not only his fellow soldiers , but his leadership","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"that wanted the best for him and for our country , ''","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"said former Army Staff Sgt . Justin Gerleve ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"who was Bergdahl 's squad leader","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Some soldiers","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"involved in operations","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"to find Bergdahl","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"have said","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"at least six soldiers were killed","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"searching for him .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Asked about this point ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Defense Secretary Chuck Hagel told reporters Wednesday","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"that he did not know of specific circumstances or details of soldiers","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"dying","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"as a result of the efforts","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"to find Bergdahl .","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"Gerleve told `` The Lead ''","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"that he believes","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Bergdahl is at least partly to blame for the soldiers ' deaths .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"`` I ca n't really say","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"I blame Bergdahl to fullest extent ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"but","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"if he would n't have deserted us ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"these soldiers very well could have been in a different place at a different time , ''","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"An Army fact-finding investigation","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"conducted in the months after Bergdahl 's 2009 disappearance","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"concluded","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"that he left his outpost deliberately and on his own free will ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"according to a U.S. military official","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"briefed on the report .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"The official spoke to CNN on Tuesday on the condition of anonymity due to the sensitive nature of the information .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"There was no definitive finding","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Bergdahl deserted","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"because that would require knowing his intent","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"-- something","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Army officials could n't do","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"without talking to the soldier .","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"On Wednesday , a U.S. official said","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"that commanders referred to Bergdahl as a `` good soldier '' in that initial fact-finding report ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"and that fellow soldiers said","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"he 'd left the post on other occasions .","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"The official ,","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"who has been briefed on the investigation ,","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"the report said","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"that Bergdahl had mailed his computer and other items home before his disappearance ,","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"but his motivation was unclear .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"Hagel said Wednesday","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"that it 's `` unfair '' to Bergdahl and his family to presume anything about his motivations","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"for leaving the base .","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"He reiterated","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"that the Army will conduct a review of the case .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"Hagel spoke with Bergdahl 's family via telephone Wednesday ,","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"a senior Defense official told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"The defense secretary reassured them","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"that Bergdahl would continue getting support with regard to his medical care and reintegration ,","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"and that the department was focused on their son 's health ,","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"the official said .","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"Bergdahl will remain at a U.S. Army medical center in Germany","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"until he completes treatment ,","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"a U.S. defense official there told CNN .","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"After that , Bergdahl will return to the United States","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"and go to a San Antonio military base ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"the official said .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"As the debate over Bergdahl showed no sign of slowing Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"his hometown of Hailey , Idaho , canceled a `` Bowe is Back '' event","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"planned to celebrate his return `` in the interest of public safety . '' Organizers ,","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"the city said ,","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"expected a large number of supporters and protesters","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"to increase attendance .","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"`` Hailey , a town of 8,000 , does not have the infrastructure","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"to support an event of the size","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"this could become , ''","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"the city said .","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"Bergdahl 's captors handed him over to the United States in exchange for the release of five prisoners","depth":3},{"id":196,"text":"held at Guantanamo Bay , Cuba .","depth":3},{"id":197,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"Hagel :","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"'Unfair ' to judge Bergdahl","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"MUST WATCH Hagel :","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"'Unfair ' to judge Bergdahl","depth":7},{"id":203,"text":"00:59","depth":5},{"id":204,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"Officials :","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"Clinton wanted tougher deal","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":209,"text":"Officials :","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"Clinton wanted tougher deal","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"05:20","depth":6},{"id":212,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"Sen. Collins :","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"Detainees are dangerous","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":217,"text":"Sen. Collins :","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"Detainees are dangerous","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"02:20","depth":8},{"id":220,"text":"Both Democrats and Republicans have criticized the deal ,","depth":6},{"id":221,"text":"arguing","depth":7},{"id":222,"text":"that it puts American lives at risk","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"by releasing terrorists","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"and accusing Obama of breaking the law","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"by not notifying Congress 30 days in advance","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"Administration officials have said","depth":7},{"id":227,"text":"they consulted the Justice Department","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"and acted legally .","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"But some Republican lawmakers have said","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"they 're not buying that argument ,","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"and want proof","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"that Bergdahl 's health was really in jeopardy .","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"`` This American is going home to his family , ''","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"Sen. Marco Rubio told CNN 's `` The Situation Room ''","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"before heading into a classified Senate briefing on Bergdahl on Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"`` These five members of the Taliban are going back to the battlefield . ''","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"`` I remain increasingly convinced","depth":10},{"id":238,"text":"that the President has now set a precedent","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"that will encourage enemies of the United States to target American men and women in uniform , ''","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":241,"text":"Rep. Debbie Wasserman Schultz , chairwoman of the Democratic National Committee , said","depth":6},{"id":242,"text":"criticism from lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"who 'd long been pushing for Obama to help bring Bergdahl home","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"is `` disingenuous . '' `` We had intelligence , from everything","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"that I understand ...","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"that this was our last , best opportunity ,","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"that he was potentially on death 's door .","depth":11},{"id":248,"text":"Looking at grainy video is not a way for us","depth":11},{"id":249,"text":"to determine that .","depth":11},{"id":250,"text":"But from everything","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"I understand ,","depth":12},{"id":252,"text":"this was our last best opportunity , ''","depth":11},{"id":253,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":254,"text":"John Bellinger , a former State Department legal adviser in President George W. Bush 's administration , told CNN","depth":7},{"id":255,"text":"that the prisoner swap deal was `` defensible . ''","depth":7},{"id":256,"text":"`` This is one of those tough national security situations","depth":9},{"id":257,"text":"that presidents face , ''","depth":9},{"id":258,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":259,"text":"`` where all the options are bad . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":519,"left":454,"right":518,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":454,"left":278,"right":453,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":262,"right":277,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":0,"right":261,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":261,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":277,"left":266,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":264,"right":265,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":263,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":269,"right":275,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":267,"right":268,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":272,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":12,"right":271,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":13,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":16,"right":273,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":453,"left":290,"right":452,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":281,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":22,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":279,"right":21,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa